n Society, Inc.\n| url = https://www.marxists.org/history/usa/pubs/laborage/v21n06-jun-1932-labor-age.pdf\n| date = June 1932\n| accessdate = 29 June 2019}}</ref>\n* \"After Roosevelt - What?\" ''Colliers'' (~1932-1934)<ref>\n{{cite web\n| first1=Benjamin \n| last1=Mandel\n| authorlink = Benjamin Mandel\n| title = After Roosevelt - What?\n| publisher = (unknown)\n| url = http://www.oac.cdlib.org/findaid/ark:/13030/tf629004p8/entire_text/\n| date = August 1928\n| accessdate = 4 March 2018}}</ref>\n* \"Evaluation of the World Trade Union Federation\" (1946?)<ref>\n{{cite web\n| first1=Benjamin \n| last1=Mandel\n| authorlink = Benjamin Mandel\n| title = Evaluation of the World Trade Union Federation\n| publisher = (unknown)\n| url = https://oac.cdlib.org/view?docId=c8jw8d64;view=dsc;style=oac4;doc.view=entire_text;dsc.position=10001;dsc.position=5001\n| date = 2018\n| accessdate = 4 March 2018}}</ref>\n* \"A Handbook for Americans:  The Communist Party:  What It Is, How It Works\" (1955)<ref name=WPobit /><ref>\n{{cite web\n| title = A Handbook for Americans: The Communist Party: What It Is, How It Works\n| publisher = US GPO\n| url = https://archive.org/details/communistpartyof1955unit\n| date = 1955\n| accessdate = 3 March 2018}}</ref>\n\n==See also==\n\n* [[Communist Party of the United States of America]]\n* [[Jay Lovestone]]\n* [[Teachers Union]]\n* [[J.B. Matthews]]\n* [[House Un-American Activities Committee]]\n* [[United States Senate Subcommittee on Internal Security|Senate Internal Security Subcommittee]]\n* [[Whittaker Chambers]]\n* [[Alger Hiss]]\n\n== References ==\n\n{{Reflist}}\n\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Mandel, Benjamin}}\n[[Category:Right Opposition]]\n[[Category:American communists]]\n[[Category:American anti-communists]]\n[[Category:1891 births]]\n[[Category:1973 deaths]]\n[[Category:McCarthyism]]\n[[Category:American schoolteachers]]\n[[Category:20th-century American educators]]\n[[Category:Members of the Communist Party USA]]\n", "na